{"thag6.2:0.1":"Theragatha 6.2 ","thag6.2:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.2:0.4":"Tekicchakarittheragatha ","thag6.2:1.1":"“Atihita vihi, ","thag6.2:1.2":"khalagata sali; ","thag6.2:1.3":"Na ca labhe pindam, ","thag6.2:1.4":"kathamaham kassam”. ","thag6.2:2.1":"“Buddhamappameyyam anussara pasanno, ","thag6.2:2.2":"Pitiya phutasariro hohisi satatamudaggo. ","thag6.2:3.1":"Dhammamappameyyam anussara pasanno, ","thag6.2:3.2":"Pitiya phutasariro hohisi satatamudaggo. ","thag6.2:4.1":"Sanghamappameyyam anussara pasanno, ","thag6.2:4.2":"Pitiya phutasariro hohisi satatamudaggo”. ","thag6.2:5.1":"“Abbhokase viharasi, ","thag6.2:5.2":"Sita hemantika ima ratyo; ","thag6.2:5.3":"Ma sitena pareto vihannittho, ","thag6.2:5.4":"Pavisa tvam viharam phusitaggalam”. ","thag6.2:6.1":"“Phusissam catasso appamannayo, ","thag6.2:6.2":"Tahi ca sukhito viharissam; ","thag6.2:6.3":"Naham sitena vihannissam, ","thag6.2:6.4":"Aninjito viharanto”ti. ","thag6.2:6.5":"… Tekicchakari thero …. "}